Missouri_City.KZJL:
KZJL, virtual channel 61 (UHF digital channel 44), is an Estrella TV owned-and-operated television station licensed to Houston, Texas, United States. Owned by Liberman Broadcasting, KZJL maintains studio facilities located on Bering Drive on the city's southwest side, and its transmitter is located near Missouri City, in unincorporated northeastern Fort Bend County.


== History ==
The station first signed on the air on June 2, 1995, as an affiliate of home shopping network Shop at Home.
